title: Pa Houa discusses being Hmong American

media:group.media:title: Pa Houa discusses being Hmong American
media:group.media:description:
Pa Houa, a participant in our “Being Asian in America” documentary, discusses being Hmong American and what differentiates Hmong people from other Asian groups. 

This video is part of our “Being Asian in America” project. 
Watch the full documentary here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LIIvqJDv6_4 
For more on the project, visit https://www.pewresearch.org/BeingAsianInAmerica
